\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 02, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xna1665702718729.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xna1665702718729.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xna1665702718729.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xna1665702718729\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set one or more license management options, according to your Sentinel license\n      type.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xna1665702718729__topic_d140921e1_d140922e1_d140923e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xna1665702718729__p_d140924e1_d140925e1_d140926e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LICENSE_OPTIONS</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>}\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>}<sup class=\"ph sup\">n</sup>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xna1665702718729__p_d140927e1_d140928e1_d140929e1\">where <var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var> is one of:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xna1665702718729__li_d49763e1_d49764e1_d49765e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_LICENSE_FILE</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LicenseServers</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">LicenseFile</var> |\n                  <var class=\"keyword varname\">CloudConfigFile</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">LicenseDir</var>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xna1665702718729__li_d49766e1_d49767e1_d49768e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_NOTIFICATION</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NumberOfDays</var>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xna1665702718729__li_d49769e1_d49770e1_d49771e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_TRANSCRIPT</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NumberOfDays</var>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_LOGFILE</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NumberOfDays</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">true</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">false</var>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xna1665702718729__li_d49772e1_d49773e1_d49774e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_RENEWAL_NOTIFICATION</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NumberOfDays</var>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xna1665702718729__li_d49775e1_d49776e1_d49777e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_MAINTENANCE_NOTIFICATION</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NumberOfDays</var>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xna1665702718729__li_d49778e1_d49779e1_d49780e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xna1665702718729__li_d49781e1_d49782e1_d49783e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_LOAD =</code>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">S</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">sentinel</code> |\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">snt</code> } | {<code class=\"ph codeph\">C</code>} {<code class=\"ph codeph\">R</code>}\n                  {<code class=\"ph codeph\">G</code>} {<code class=\"ph codeph\">9</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">10</code>} </li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_UPGRADE_NOTIFICATION</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NumberOfDays</var>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_COMMUTER_NOTIFICATION</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NumberOfDays</var>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_TIMEOUT</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Seconds</var></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_REDUNDANT</code></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xna1665702718729__section_y3d_vtb_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d710802e234\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xna1665702718729__table_d16874e1_d16875e1_d16876e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Items</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Value</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\">Assignment file</td>\n<td class=\"entry\">Application assignment files </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xna1665702718729__section_obk_gvb_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d710802e291\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xna1665702718729__p_d140936e1_d140937e1_d140938e1\">Uniface makes use of the Sentinel Rights Management\n            System (RMS) to manage licensing. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nzw1665702745583.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nzw1665702745583.html\" title=\"Uniface makes use of Sentinel to handle licensing of Uniface products.\">Uniface License Management</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xna1665702718729__p_d140939e1_d140940e1_d140941e1\">For existing\n            Uniface Enterprise Edition users, it is still possible to use the Uniface Distributed\n            License Manager (DLM) up to version 10.3.03. If no Sentinel options are selected, DLM is\n            used by default.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xna1665702718729__p_d140942e1_d140943e1_d140944e1\">For DLM\n            license configuration, see $LICENSE_OPTIONS (DLM).</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_NOTIFICATION</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_RENEWAL_NOTIFICATION</code>,\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_MAINTENANCE_NOTIFICATION</code>,\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_UPGRADE_NOTIFICATION</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_COMMUTER_NOTIFICATION</code>,\n            and <code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE</code> settings overrides\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_TRANSCRIPT</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_LOGFILE</code> settings if they are\n            set to a lower value.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533802\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533802\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$LICENSE_OPTIONS Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 02, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set one or more license management options, according to your Sentinel license type. $LICENSE_OPTIONS { = } Option { , Option } n where Option is one of: LM_LICENSE_FILE = LicenseServers | LicenseFile | CloudConfigFile | LicenseDir LM_NOTIFICATION = NumberOfDays LM_TRANSCRIPT = NumberOfDays LM_LOGFILE = NumberOfDays | true | false LM_RENEWAL_NOTIFICATION = NumberOfDays LM_MAINTENANCE_NOTIFICATION = NumberOfDays LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE LM_LOAD = { S | sentinel | snt } | { C } { R } { G } { 9 | 10 } LM_UPGRADE_NOTIFICATION = NumberOfDays LM_COMMUTER_NOTIFICATION = NumberOfDays LM_TIMEOUT = Seconds LM_REDUNDANT Defaults Items Value Assignment file Application assignment files Section [SETTINGS] Default value None Description Uniface makes use of the Sentinel Rights Management System (RMS) to manage licensing. For more information, see Uniface License Management . For existing Uniface Enterprise Edition users, it is still possible to use the Uniface Distributed License Manager (DLM) up to version 10.3.03. If no Sentinel options are selected, DLM is used by default. For DLM license configuration, see $LICENSE_OPTIONS (DLM). LM_NOTIFICATION , LM_RENEWAL_NOTIFICATION , LM_MAINTENANCE_NOTIFICATION , LM_UPGRADE_NOTIFICATION , LM_COMMUTER_NOTIFICATION , and LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE settings overrides LM_TRANSCRIPT and LM_LOGFILE settings if they are set to a lower value. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}